---
title: Herby Tabbouleh Salad with Garlic Couscous | Serves 2
description: Try our version of a Middle Eastern staple – tabbouleh! Garlic-infused couscous is a hearty addition to this herb-flecked salad, while the squeeze of lemon juice adds a delightful zing to this side dish.

